gores norment holdings inc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Asset Management
Sub-Industry: Private Equity
Gores Norment Holdings, Inc. operates as a private equity firm. The Company invests in technology, telecommunications, business services, industrial, healthcare, media and entertainment, and consumer products industries. Gores Norment Holdings serves customers worldwide.




